      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HUNGER STRIKE (1) has been coming from wider or second row barriers of late and producing some good efforts including a third after racing parked two back at this circuit and distance. She looks well served by the ace draw. Leading hope. Hard to knock the recent consistency of FULL SWING DENARIO NZ (2) who has put together a string of placings. Raced parked but fought well to miss by a head here last week. Should enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position so could break through. SPITFIRE (10) is another with the hoof on the till after three straight placings at this circuit and distance including a third from this barrier last week. Go well again. CHACO EAGLE (6) is working towards a win having come from this barrier for a respectable second at his most recent appearance here.",
